In the city of [[Neverwinter]], scallops could be found cooked wrapped in [[bacon]].

Scallops were served at [[Sharkey's Bar & Grill]] in the city of [[Ravens Bluff]], priced at a single [[silver]] per six scallops.{{Cite polyhedron/79/The Living City: The Painted Boat Restaurant|17}}

A giant variety was known to exit and their shells were used to craft large trays.
